highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs USA. “Nobody’s Son” is the highest at #9.
“Here With Me” by d4vd is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs USA, up 37 spots at #39.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs USA the longest, at 89 days straight.
“Where Have You Been x No Pole” by rudo made it and COSKO is the highest new entry on Viral Songs USA at #8.
